content.query:
IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM sys.external_file_formats WHERE name = 'SynapseParquetFormat') 
	CREATE EXTERNAL FILE FORMAT [SynapseParquetFormat] 
	WITH ( FORMAT_TYPE = PARQUET)
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM sys.external_data_sources WHERE name = 'synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net') 
	CREATE EXTERNAL DATA SOURCE [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net] 
	WITH (
		LOCATION = 'abfss://synapse@citylogisticsstorage.dfs.core.windows.net' 
	)
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE F_CTS_O_DispatchMonthTotals (
	[dispatch.did] bigint,
	[dispatch.id] bigint,
	[dispatch.lmsid] bigint,
	[dispatch.distance] bigint,
	[dispatch.duration] bigint,
	[dispatch.expdistance] bigint,
	[dispatch.expduration] bigint,
	[dispatch.vehicletype] int,
	[Vehicle_Type] nvarchar(4000),
	[NUM_Delivery] bigint,
	[dispatch_id] bigint,
	[delivery_deliverydate] date,
	[NUM_Parcels] bigint,
	[delivery_status] nvarchar(4000)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Facts/CTS/F_CTS_O_DispatchMonthTotals.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.F_CTS_O_DispatchMonthTotals
GO
